    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This 987.1 Cayman S features the robust 3.4L M97 flat-six powerplant paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle. The mid-engine configuration ensures a neutral handling balance, further enhanced by a factory-optioned PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) system. Recent preventative maintenance includes a high-flow Air-Oil Separator (AOS) and a water pump replacement to ensure thermal efficiency. The hydraulic steering rack provides unadulterated feedback, while the four-piston Monobloc calipers offer consistent biting point and modulation. This is a driver-focused example with a clean bore-scope report and crisp gear engagement, ideal for the technical purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
