    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive shape both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep shine with only minor blemishes typical of careful road use, while the smoke-free interior features supple seating and fully functional technology. Mechanically, it is sound, having undergone regular servicing with a documented history. It drives smoothly, shifts crisply, and offers the perfect blend of performance and comfort for a discerning new owner looking for a reliable, high-quality daily driver.",
