    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's looking for a great new home! It\u2019s been a fantastic ride for me\u2014super reliable and still looks wonderful inside and out. It handles beautifully on the road and has been well cared for over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this beauty is ready to go. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
